<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no">
    {squarespace-headers}
  </head>
  <body id="{squarespace.page-id}" class="{squarespace.page-classes}">

    <div class="site-container">

      <header class="site-header">
        <squarespace:navigation navigationId="siteNav" template="site-navigation" />        
      </header>

    <section id="forRestaurantsSection1" >
        <div class="flex-center-center">
        <div class="flex-end-end big-phone-container">
        <img
            src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/6450698409f0fa360c02e549/fc84cddb-4695-42bb-9f38-b7d5d8a5dff2/mockup-mapview.png?content-type=image%2Fpng"
            style="height: 80%; width: auto;"
        />
        </div>
        <div id="restaurant-landing-header-title" style="width: calc(100% - 120px); ">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; color: white; opacity: 0.65; font-size: 14px;">MyMeal for Restaurants</p>
        <h1 style="color: white; padding-bottom: 15px;" class="big-titles">We make food allergies your superpower.</h1>
        
        <p style="color: white; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px;">
            We don't want you to miss out on the opportunity to gain a loyal
            customer for life. Especially when there's over 32 million of them looking
            for you.
        </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    </section>

    <section id="forRestaurantsSection2">
        <h2>Why offer an allergen menu?</h2>
        <p style="text-align: center;">Our filterable allergy menus put you and your staff back in control so you can feel confident serving any customer that comes your way.</p>
        <div class="flex-center-center icon-text-wrapper">
                <div class="icon-text flex-center-center flex-column">
                    <img class="icon" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/6450698409f0fa360c02e549/0088e021-3489-4a6a-b3a0-15f532198458/brand1.png?content-type=image%2Fpng" alt="heart icon"/>
                    <p><strong>Customer Loyalty</strong><br />
                        <span class="blue-text">92% of guests with food allergies</span>
                        will return frequently after having a positive experience eating
                        out.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="icon-text flex-center-center flex-column" style="background: #f5f5f5;">
                    <img class="icon" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/6450698409f0fa360c02e549/bd9c6604-817d-426d-bac5-02c7eb06a54b/growth.png?content-type=image%2Fpng" alt="growth icon"/>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Boost in Revenue</strong> <br />
                        Accommodating allergic guests can
                        <span class="blue-text">boost your restaurant's profit margin by 24%</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="icon-text flex-center-center flex-column">
                    <img class="icon" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/6450698409f0fa360c02e549/cd87c42f-13a7-4904-8f64-b958fb64f5f7/shield.png?content-type=image%2Fpng" alt="growth icon"/>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Avoid a Lawsuit</strong> <br />
                        Nearly 50% of food allergy related fatalities
                        <span class="blue-text">occur in eating establishments.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="forRestaurantsSection3">

        <div class="perk-container-header flex-center-center flex-column" >
            <h1 style="color: white; text-align: center; font-weight: 600; ">
                <span style="font-weight: 400; ">Create a positive experience.</span> Every time. 
            </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-center-center flex-column perk-wrapper box-shadow">
    
            <div class="perk-container flex-center-center" style="margin-top: 25px;">
                <div class="perk-text">
                    <h2>An <span class="blue-text">easy addition</span> to your menu</h2>
                    <p>We provide a QR code that links to your allergy menu. It can be accessed on a printed menu, a sticker on your table, table tents - the possibilities are endless.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="perk-image">
                    <img src="https://findmymeal.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/one-one.png" alt="example of mymeal menu aside another restaurants" >
                </div>      
            </div>

            <div class="perk-container flex-center-center">
                <div class="perk-image">
                    <img src="https://findmymeal.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/two-two-two.png" alt="example of filterable allergy menus" >
                </div>
                <div class="perk-text">
                    <h2>Allergens made <span class="blue-text">simple</span></h2>
                    <p>When a customer comes in with multiple allergens, it is stressful for your staff to offer recommendations. With MyMeal, your customer can filter your menu by any allergen your kitchen can accommodate.</p><br>
                    <a href="https://mymealmenus.com/order/restaurants/12/locations/9" target="_blank" class="styled-button hover">View a Demo Menu Page</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="perk-container flex-center-center">
                <div class="perk-text">
                    <h2>We protect you from <span class="blue-text">lawsuits</span></h2>
                    <p>We get it. Catering to people with allergies can seem scary. Thatâ€™s why we have a disclaimer that notifies the customer of your ever changing ingredient list and shared kitchen.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="perk-image">
                    <img src="https://findmymeal.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/three-three.png" alt="example of mymeal menu aside another restaurants">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="perk-container flex-center-center">
                <div class="perk-image" >
                    <img src="https://findmymeal.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/callouts2.png" alt="example of mymeal menu aside another restaurants">
                </div>
                <div class="perk-text" >
                    <h2>Saves your staff <span class="blue-text">time and mistakes</span> </h2>
                    <p>Ditch the back and forth conversation between your chef and server. We hash out modification and cross contact information for each dish with your chef. </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div id="last-perk-container">
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <img src="assets/sparkles.png" style="width: 100px;"/>
            </div>
            <h1 class="blue-text" style="text-align: center;">
                <span style="font-weight: 300;">We provide a transparent, stress-free experience for both parties</span>- creating loyal customers and saving your restaurant time.
            </h1>
            <p style="color: rgba(0,0,0,0.65); text-align: center">Documenting the allergens in each of your dishes is a time sink. That's why our certified nutrition specialists do it for you. We fix mistakes within 75% of the restaurants we work with, ensuring your staff and guests have positive interactions start to finish.</p>
            <div class="flex-center-center">
                <a class="blue-outline-button" href="#restaurant-scheduler-container">Request a Demo</a>
            </div>
        </div>


    </section>

    <section id="forRestaurantsSection4">
        <h1 style="padding: 25px;" class="blue-text">
            <span style="font-weight: 400; color: black;">Oh yeah, did we mention</span> free marketing?
        </h1>
        <div id="reels-gif-container" class="flex-center-center"></div>
        <h4>
            MyMeal has an active community of over 10,000+ members on social media and a user base that grows 9% every week.<br> The one thing our followers have in
            common? <span class="blue-text bold">They want to eat out and feel safe.</span> <br />
            <br />
            As a partner, we will promote you on the MyMeal app and to our social media pages, <span class="blue-text bold">for free. </span>
        </h4>
        <button onclick="togglePopup()" style=" width: 300px;" class="styled-button">Download the MyMeal App</button>
    </section>

    <section id="forRestaurantsSection5" class="flex-center-center flex-column">
            <h2 style="color: white; text-align: center; padding: 25px 15px;">Flexible, easy-to-use technology built by listening to restaurant owners.</h2>
            <div id="rounded-block-container" class="flex-start-center flex-wrap">
                <div class="rounded-block flex-start-end box-shadow" id="rounded-block-first">
                    <div class="rounded-block-text">
                        <h3>Break Up with Allergen Charts</h3>
                        <p>I'm guessing you label GF and VG on the menu. Or maybe you have an allergen chart. These resources are.. </p>
                        <ul style="margin-left: 15px;">
                            <li>hard to use</li>
                            <li>labeled incorrectly</li>
                            <li>don't tell the customer the whole story</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-block flex-start-end box-shadow" id="rounded-block-second">
                    <div class="rounded-block-text">
                        <h3 class="rounded-block-title">What About Menu Changes?</h3>
                        <p>Almost all the restaurants we work with change their menu seasonally. This is why we..</p>
                        
                        <ul>
                            <li>reach out every quarter for menu updates</li>
                            <li>offer a portal to edit menu items at any time</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-center-center hover" style="width: 100%; margin-top: 15px;">
                <a id="show-me-link" href="#restaurant-scheduler-container" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Show me how &rarr;</a>
            </div>
    </section>

    <section id="forRestaurantsSection6">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 50px;">
            <img src="assets/restaurant-icon.png" style="width: 100px; padding-bottom: 15px;"/>
        </div>
        <h2 class="blue-text" style="text-align: center; padding: 0px 50px;">
            <span style="font-weight: 300;">Join dozens of restaurants who have tapped into the</span> market of over 32 million people with food allergens. 
        </h2>
        <div class="flex-center-center" >
            <a href="https://www.foodallergy.org/resources/facts-and-statistics" style="text-align: center; color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5); font-size: 10px;" target="_blank">Food Allergy Research & Education. (n.d.).</a>
        </div>

        <div class="slider">
            <div class="slide-track">
                <div class="slide flex-center-center" onclick="window.open('https://www.illegalpetes.com/')">
                    <img src="assets/restaurants/illegal-petes-logo-circle.png" alt="Illegal Petes Logo" style="height: 120px; "/>
                </div>
                <div class="slide flex-center-center" onclick="window.open('https://dagabicucina.com/')">
                    <img src="assets/restaurants/dagabi-black.png" alt="Dagabi Cucina Logo" style="height: 100px;"/>
                </div>
                <div class="slide flex-center-center" onclick="window.open('https://hornetrestaurant.com/')">
                    <img src="assets/restaurants/hornet.png" style="height: 110px;" alt="Hornet Denver Logo"/>
                </div>
                <div class="slide flex-center-center" onclick="window.open('https://www.bluebonnetrestaurant.com/')">
                    <img src="assets/restaurants/blue-bonnet-logo.png" style="height: 120px;" alt="Blue Bonnet Logo"/>
                </div>
                <div class="slide flex-center-center" onclick="window.open('https://www.parkergarage.com/')">
                    <img src="assets/restaurants/parker-garage-logo.png" style="height: 60px;" alt="Parker Garage Logo"/>
                </div>
                <div class="slide flex-center-center" onclick="window.open('https://wholesol.com/')">
                    <img src="assets/restaurants/wholesol.png" style="height: 100px;" alt="Whole Sol Logo" />
                </div>
                <div class="slide flex-center-center" onclick="window.open('https://www.teocallicocina.com/')">
                    <img src="assets/restaurants/teocalli.avif" style="height: 80px;" alt="Teocalli Cocina Logo"/>
                </div>
                <div class="slide flex-center-center" onclick="window.open('https://acovarestaurant.com/')">
                    <img src="assets/restaurants/acova.jpeg" style="height: 120px;" alt="Acova Logo"/>
                </div>
                <div class="slide" onclick="window.open('https://www.foragedrestaurant.com/')">
                    <img src="assets/restaurants/Foraged_Logo_Kitchen_Rawbar.png" style="height: 120px;" alt="Foraged Denver Logo"/>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


      
      <!-- cms content injection point -->
      <main class="content-container" role="main" data-content-field="main-content" >
       {squarespace.main-content}
      </main>

      <!--Footer with open block field -->
      <footer class="site-footer">
        <squarespace:block-field id="footerBlocks" columns="12" />
      </footer>

    </div>

    <!-- combo and minify scripts when not logged in -->
    <squarespace:script src="site.js" combo="{.if authenticatedAccount}false{.or}true{.end}" />

    <!-- other scripts, and footer code injection -->
    {squarespace-footers}

  </body>
</html>


